f07e343fecde", "title": "{NEW} FIAS Remake Dev Team Application", "description": "This form is for people who want to help make a remake of Fight in a School (FIAS) on Roblox. Read EVERYTHING carefully before applying.", "style": "wii_u_menu", "maxResponses": 100, "maxAcceptedResponses": 20, "createdAt": 1775091541528, "updatedAt": 1775092777006, "questions": [{"id": "85a26255-8bb4-4438-8fb8-f1c51708fa8d", "type": "note", "label": "DEV RULE SHEET", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "REQUIRED RULES: You MUST join the Discord server https://discord.gg/QbCDbkd4v . There are TWO separate games (Coding/Animating/UI and Building). You MUST actually work and show real progress. Doing small or lazy work (like placing a few toolbox items and leaving) is NOT allowed. If you are inactive for more than 3 weeks you will be removed, blacklisted from the game, and banned from the server. Blacklist means no access to the game at all including alternate accounts. When working you MUST join the \"working on game\" voice channel and screen share the entire time. You MUST take screenshots when you JOIN and when you LEAVE the voice channel as proof. The system logs EVERYTHING including opening, editing, testing, or doing anything. If you are working and NOT in the voice channel you will be punished. Voice Channel Link: https://discord.com/channels/1482562979177431223/1488651165423112232", "referenceCode": "FIAS-DEV-RULES", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "fac70c7b-fda5-47f5-be3f-c519ca22b9da", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "IMPORTANT RULES: There are TWO separate games. One is for Coding, Animating, UI, and systems. The other is for Building and map design.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "e9f693e9-b25c-40c5-a0f5-148e9a148194", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "You MUST join the Discord server: https://discord.gg/QbCDbkd4v", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "b5e3fada-ddbd-4f25-b181-7d6992c5a647", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "You are REQUIRED to actually WORK on the game. You cannot sit in the server waiting for admin, roles, or benefits.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "d25d098c-7b05-48e1-8ec6-405fa365d06b", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "Lazy work is NOT allowed. You cannot just place a few toolbox items and leave. I MUST see real effort and progress.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "c55c4f29-45bb-4250-92cc-dceacb349439", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "I must see real progress. If you do not work for more than 3 weeks, you will be removed.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "72e473aa-8307-4c02-b1e4-8695ccdcc178", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "If you join the game in Studio and do nothing, it will still be logged and treated as inactivity.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "03852a19-ca9e-46fa-95c1-d817f824c1a6", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "Consequences: removal, blacklist from the game, and ban from the Discord server.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "7f931bd8-b54e-4173-8d99-90f7ace6e9a1", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "Blacklist means you will not be able to access the game at all, including alternate accounts.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "f3157181-4640-420e-a83f-351d4c5a726e", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "When working, you MUST join the \"working on game\" voice channel and screen share the entire time.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "5828a70b-2f8a-4128-8d38-af84dfedd8e6", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "You MUST take screenshots when you JOIN and when you LEAVE the voice channel as proof.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "4bd9ce32-a6e3-466b-b8c3-200142093f95", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "The system logs everything including opening, editing, testing, or doing anything in the game.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "15c28029-e98d-4409-8b6b-dcd36d965006", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "If you are working and NOT in the voice channel, you will be punished.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "5d63a14f-e6c0-4a51-9a4f-60d47cbf2f99", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "Voice Channel Link (JOIN \"working on game\" ONLY): https://discord.com/channels/1482562979177431223/14