atch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ   \n\n\n\n\n\n\nps: I could not find a working video that shows how.\n\nAll jokes aside though!", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "b2e7a63f-d4d8-40af-954c-65814a3a97dd", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "Some Roblox age groups may restrict collaboration. If your account has restrictions, you may need to use a trusted connection setting.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "aa807198-6f6f-4a93-9fe1-8aa2a598306f", "type": "text", "label": "Imported Text", "required": false, "options": [], "placeholder": "", "content": "If you know how to set trusted connections on Roblox, you may still be allowed. If not, it may limit your ability to join.", "referenceCode": "", "branches": [{"match": "Option 1", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 2", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 3", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 4", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 5", "prompts": []}, {"match": "Option 6", "prompts": []}], "graphPoints": [{"label": "A", "value": 4}, {"label": "B", "value": 7}, {"label": "C", "value": 5}], "scaleLeft": "Low", "scaleRight": "High"}, {"id": "e4d694e3-0d8b-4550-ba64-b26d5ebdf595", "type": "short", "label": "What is your Roblo